egration depth, and workforce adoption\\\" },\\n114 |     { phase: \\\"PHASE 4\\\", title: \\\"Autonomous Enterprise\\\", time: \\\"18+ Months\\\", focus: \\\"Cross-functional agent orchestration at enterprise scale\\\" },\\n115 |   ],\\n116 |   insights: {\\n117 |     summary: \\\"A balanced AI enterprise blueprint designed to scale intelligent agents across your operating model, architecture, and governance layers.\\\",\\n118 |     recommendations: [\\n119 |       \\\"Start with intelligent workforce capabilities as the anchor for your first production agents.\\\",\\n120 |       \\\"Deploy agents in waves, prioritizing workflow automation in phase one.\\\",\\n121 |       \\\"Align architecture investments to your existing systems landscape before scaling.\\\",\\n122 |       \\\"Establish trust and governance controls as the non-negotiable baseline for every agent release.\\\",\\n123 |     ],\\n124 |     agentEcosystemDetail: \\\"24 agents recommended across workflow, service, and analytics domains to support enterprise-wide AI transformation.\\\",\\n125 |     architectureDetail: \\\"A layered architecture spanning data & intelligence, AI & agent, orchestration, and integration layers — designed for composable enterprise scale.\\\",\\n126 |     governanceDetail: \\\"Governance should emphasize trust, risk, security, compliance, and ethics before broad rollout across the organization.\\\",\\n127 |     transformationNotes: [\\n128 |       \\\"Phase timelines reflect a typical enterprise transformation cadence.\\\",\\n129 |       \\\"Success metrics should track operational impact within the first 90 days.\\\",\\n130 |       \\\"Generate a personalized blueprint by completing all inputs on the left.\\\",\\n131 |     ],\\n132 |   },\\n133 | };\\n134 | \\n135 | const industryOperatingModel: Record<string, string[]> = {\\n136 |   \\\"financial-services\\\": [\\\"Regulated Agent Workflows\\\", \\\"Fraud & Compliance Intelligence\\\", \\\"Client Service Copilots\\\", \\\"Risk-Aware Decisioning\\\"],\\n137 |   \\\"industry-resources\\\": [\\\"Plant Operations Copilots\\\", \\\"Predictive Asset Intelligence\\\", \\\"Supply Chain Orchestration\\\", \\\"Field Service Automation\\\"],\\n138 |   \\\"health-life-sciences\\\": [\\\"Clinical Workflow Assistants\\\", \\\"Patient Journey Intelligence\\\", \\\"Care Coordination Agents\\\", \\\"Research Acceleration\\\"],\\n139 |   \\\"public-education\\\": [\\\"Citizen Service Agents\\\", \\\"Case Routing Intelligence\\\", \\\"Learning Operations Copilots\\\", \\\"Policy-Aware Automation\\\"],\\n140 |   \\\"consumer-digital\\\": [\\\"Customer Experience Agents\\\", \\\"Commerce Intelligence\\\", \\\"Support Automation\\\", \\\"Personalization Engines\\\"],\\n141 | };\\n142 | \\n143 | const goalAgents: Record<string, { count: number; types: string[] }> = {\\n144 |   efficiency: { count: 18, types: [\\\"Process Automation Agents\\\", \\\"Document Intelligence Agents\\\", \\\"Ops Copilots\\\"] },\\n145 |   \\\"customer-experience\\\": { count: 22, types: [\\\"Service Agents\\\", \\\"Journey Orchestration Agents\\\", \\\"Sentiment Intelligence Agents\\\"] },\\n146 |   automation: { count: 28, types: [\\\"Workflow Agents\\\", \\\"Integration Agents\\\", \\\"Task Orchestration Agents\\\"] },\\n147 |   innovation: { count: 24, types: [\\\"Product Discovery Agents\\\", \\\"Rapid Prototype Agents\\\", \\\"Market Intelligence Agents\\\"] },\\n148 |   \\\"decision-intelligence\\\": { count: 20, types: [\\\"Analytics Agents\\\", \\\"Forecasting Agents\\\", \\\"Executive Briefing Agents\\\"] },\\n149 | };\\n150 | \\n151 | const systemArchitecture: Record<string, string[]> = {\\n152 |   legacy: [\\\"Integration Gateway Layer\\\", \\\"Legacy System Connectors\\\", \\\"AI & Agent Layer\\\", \\\"Governed Data Fabric\\\"],\\n153 |   hybrid: [\\\"Hybrid Integration Layer\\\", \\\"Cloud & On-Prem Bridge\\\", \\\"AI & Agent Layer\\\", \\\"Unified Intelligence Layer\\\"],\\n154 |   \\\"cloud-native\\\": [\\\"API-First Integration Layer\\\", \\\"Event-Driven Orchestration\\\", \\\"AI & Agent Layer\\\", \\\"Scalable Data Platform\\\"],\\n155 |   fragmented: [\\\"Enterprise Integration Hub\\\", \\\"Master Data Harmonization\\\", \\\"AI & Agent Layer\\\", \\\"Cross-System Orchestration\\\"],\\n156 | };\\n157 | \\n158 | const riskGovernance: Record<string, string[]> = {\\n159 |   conservative: [\\\"Strict Model Governance\\\", \\\"Human-in-the-Loop Controls\\\", \\\"Audit & Compliance Trails\\\", \\\"Ethics Review Board\\\"],\\n160 |   moderate: [\\\"Policy-Based Guardrails\\\", \\\"Risk Tiering Framework\\\", \\\"Security & Privacy Controls\\\", \\\"Responsible AI Standards\\\"],\\n161 |   aggressive: [\\\"Automated Policy Checks\\\", \\\"Rapid Release Gates\\\", \\\"Security Monitoring\\\", \\\"Ethics Guidelines\\\"],\\n162 |   experimental: [\\\"Sandbox Environments\\\", \\\"Pilot Governance\\\", \\\"Fast Feedback Loops\\\", \\\"Ethics & Safety Reviews\\\"],\\n163 | };\\n164 | \\n165 | const sizeRoadmapTiming: Record<string, [string, string, string, string]> = {\\n166 |   startup: [\\\"0-2 Months\\\", \\\"2-6 Months\\\", \\\"6-12 Months\\\", \\\"12+ Months\\\"],\\n167 |   \\\"mid-market\\\": [\\\"0-3 Months\\\", \\\"3-9 Months\\\", \\\"9-15 Months\\\", \\\"15+ Months\\\"],\\n168 |   enterprise: [\\\"0-3 Months\\\", \\\"3-9 Months\\\", \\\"9-18 Months\\\", \\\"18+ Months\\\"],\\n169 |   global: [\\\"0-4 Months\\\", \\\"4-12 Months\\\", \\\"12-24 Months\\\", \\\"24+ Months\\\"],\\n170 | };\\n171 | \\n172 | function getOptionLabel(key: BlueprintFieldKey, value: string) {\\n173 |   return blueprintFields.find((field) => field.key === key)?.options.find((option) => option.value === value)?.label ?? value;\\n174 | }\\n175 | \\n176 | export function getEmptyBlueprintAnswers(): BlueprintAnswers {\\n177 |   return {\\n178 |     industry: \\\"\\\",\\n179 |     enterpriseSize: \\\"\\\",\\n180 |     aiGoals: \\\"\\\",\\n181 |     workforceSize: \\\"\\\",\\n182 |     existingSystems: \\\"\\\",\\n183 |     riskAppetite: \\\"\\\",\\n184 |   };\\n185 | }\\n186 | \\n187 | export function isBlueprintComplete(answers: BlueprintAnswers) {\\n188 |   return blueprintFields.every((field) => Boolean(answers[field.key]));\\n189 | }\\n190 | \\n191 | export function generateBlueprint(answers: BlueprintAnswers): BlueprintResult {\\n192 |   const industry = answers.industry;\\n193 |   const operatingModel = industryOperatingModel[industry] ?? [\\\"Intelligent Workforce\\\", \\\"Agentic Automation\\\", \\\"Decision Intelligence\\\", \\\"Continuous Learning\\\"];\\n194 |   const agents = goalAgents[answers.aiGoals] ?? { count: 24, types: [\\\"Workflow Agents\\\", \\\"Service Agents\\\", \\\"Analytics Agents\\\"] };\\n195 |   const architecture = systemArchitecture[answers.existingSystems] ?? [\\\"Data & Intelligence Layer\\\", \\\"AI & Agent Layer\\\", \\\"Orchestration Layer\\\", \\\"Integration Layer\\\"];\\n196 |   const governance = riskGovernance[answers.riskAppetite] ?? [\\\"Trust\\\", \\\"Risk\\\", \\\"Security\\\", \\\"Compliance\\\", \\\"Ethics\\\"];\\n197 |   const timings = sizeRoadmapTiming[answers.enterpriseSize] ?? [\\\"0-3 Months\\\", \\\"3-9 Months\\\", \\\"9-18 Months\\\", \\\"18+ Months\\\"];\\n198 | \\n199 |   const workforceMultiplier =\\n200 |     answers.workforceSize === \\\"very-large\\\" ? 1.35 : answers.workforceSize === \\\"large\\\" ? 1.2 : answers.workforceSize === \\\"medium\\\" ? 1.05 : 1;\\n201 |   const agentCount = Math.round(agents.count * workforceMultiplier);\\n202 | \\n203 |   const industryLabel = getOptionLabel(\\\"industry\\\", industry);\\n204 |   const goalLabel = getOptionLabel(\\\"aiGoals\\\", answers.aiGoals);\\n205 |   const riskLabel = getOptionLabel(\\\"riskAppetite\\\", answers.riskAppetite);\\n206 | \\n207 |   return {\\n208 |     operatingModel,\\n209 |     agentCount,\\n210 |     agentTypes: agents.types,\\n211 |     architecture,\\n212 |     governance,\\n213 |     roadmap: [\\n214 |       { phase: \\\"PHASE 1\\\", title: \\\"Foundation\\\", time: timings[0], focus: \\\"Data readiness, governance baseline, and priority use cases\\\" },\\n215 |       { phase: \\\"PHASE 2\\\", title: \\\"Scale\\\", time: timings[1], focus: \\\"Agent deployment across high-impact workflows\\\" },\\n216 |       { phase: \\\"PHASE 3\\\", title: \\\"Optimize\\\", time: timings[2], focus: \\\"Performance tuning, integration depth, and workforce adoption\\\" },\\n217 |       { phase: \\\"PHASE 4\\\", title: \\\"Autonomous Enterprise\\\", time: timings[3], focus: \\\"Cross-functional agent orchestration at enterprise scale\\\" },\\n218 |     ],\\n219 |     insights: {\\n220 |       summary: `A ${riskLabel.toLowerCase()} AI enterprise blueprint for ${industryLabel}, designed to deliver ${goalLabel.toLowerCase()} across your organization.`,\\n221 |       recommendations: [\\n222 |         `Start with ${operatingModel[0].toLowerCase()} as the anchor capability for your first production agents.`,\\n223 |         `Deploy ${agentCount} agents in waves, prioritizing ${agents.types[0].toLowerCase()} in phase one.`,\\n224 |         `Align architecture investments to your ${getOptionLabel(\\\"existingSystems\\\", answers.existingSystems).toLowerCase()} landscape before scaling.`,\\n225 |         `Establish ${governance[0].toLowerCase()} as the non-negotiable control for every agent release.`,\\n226 |       ],\\n227 |       agentEcosystemDetail: `${agentCount} agents recommended across ${agents.types.join(\\\", \\\")}. This mix supports ${goalLabel.toLowerCase()} while matching your ${getOptionLabel(\\\"workforceSize\\\", answers.workforceSize).toLowerCase()} workforce footprint.`,\\n228 |       architectureDetail: `Your ${getOptionLabel(\\\"existingSystems\\\", answers.existingSystems).toLowerCase()} environment maps to a layered architecture: ${architecture.join(\\\" → \\\")}. Integration depth should increase in phases 2 and 3.`,\\n229 |       governanceDetail: `With a ${riskLabel.toLowerCase()} risk posture, governance should emphasize ${governance.slice(0, 3).join(\\\", \\\").toLowerCase()} before broad rollout.`,\\n230 |       transformationNotes: [\\n231 |         `${industryLabel}: prioritize industry-specific compliance and workflow patterns.`,\\n232 |         `${getOptionLabel(\\\"enterpriseSize\\\", answers.enterpriseSize)} scale: phase timelines reflect your organizational complexity.`,\\n233 |         `${goalLabel}: success metrics should track operational impact within the first 90 days.`,\\n234 |       ],\\n235 |     },\\n236 |   };\\n237 | }\\n238 | \\n239 | export function getFieldLabel(key: BlueprintFieldKey) {\\n240 |   return blueprintFields.find((field) => field.key === key)?.label ?? key;\\n241 | }\\n242 | \\n243 | export function getSelectedOptionLabel(key: BlueprintFieldKey, value: string) {\\n244 |   return getOptionLabel(key, value);\\n245 | }\\n246 | \\n247 | export function calculateBlueprintScore(input: {\\n248 |   aiMaturityScore: number;\\n249 |   businessNeedScore: number;\\n250 |   dataReadinessScore: number;\\n251 |   processComplexityScore: number;\\n252 |   transformationReadinessScore: number;\\n253 | }) {\\n254 |   const {\\n255 |     aiMaturityScore,\\n256 |     businessNeedScore,\\n257 |     dataReadinessScore,\\n258 |     processComplexityScore,\\n259 |     transformationReadinessScore,\\n260 |   } = input;\\n261 |   \\n262 |   const score = \\n263 |     (aiMaturityScore * 0.20) + \\n264 |     (businessNeedScore * 0.25) + \\n265 |     (dataReadinessScore * 0.20) + \\n266 |     (processComplexityScore * 0.20) + \\n267 |     (transformationReadinessScore * 0.15);\\n268 |     \\n269 |   return Math.round(score);\\n270 | }\\n271 | \\n272 | export function getScoreCategory(score: number) {\\n273 |   if (score <= 25) return \\\"AI Beginner\\\";\\n274 |   if (score <= 50) return \\\"AI Explorer\\\";\\n275 |   if (score <= 70) return \\\"AI Adopter\\\";\\n276 |   if (score <= 85) return \\\"AI Transformer\\\";\\n277 |   return \\\"AI-Native Le